<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">hello, my main character is a monk, but i decided to try out a bard, just for kicks.  i have some questions.<p>

how do instruments improve the bard?  what makes it different than singing?<p>

what is the difference between instruments? would i just use the drums i got from my guild forever?  why would i want to get a different kind of drums?<p>

thanks<p>

Brynnen<br>
lvl 5 bard<br>
on Rodcet Nife</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
