<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">first of all some songs require different instruments to play. there are five types of songs (percussion, wind, strings, brass and singing) you cannot play a brass song with a percussion instrument.. Most songs can actually be sung but using the required instrument for the song will give the song a greater effect. And there are also varying degrees of instrument quality. ie some percussion instruments will have a grater effect that others. So no you probably won't want to be using your hand drum forever..</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="CENTER">
